raspkali-widget (1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial Debian packaging release.
  * Floating PyQt5 widget for real-time system monitoring.
  * Configurable via /etc/raspkali-widget/config.ini.
  * Autostart via XDG autostart mechanism.
  * Process control via raspkali-widget-ctl script.

